Method Detail

getRevision

public int getRevision()
Description copied from interface: ExerciseData

Records the revision of this ExerciseData. The ViLLE system guarantees that incompatible (different revision) SubmissionInfos and ExerciseDatas are not mixed.

When an Editor is loaded with an ExerciseData-object and that object is changed in such a way that SubmissionInfo-objects corresponding to the old ExerciseData are not compatible or semantically meaningful (ie. for example if in a quiz a question was changed to something completely different, the old answer is not meaningful anymore, as the answer was given to a different question).

Specified by:
getRevision in interface ExerciseData
Returns:
revision number of this ExerciseData-object
